
<TestUnit> is a unit:
    plural is <TestUnits>
    abbreviation is "tu"

<BloodPressure> is a number:
    unit is mmHg
    valid values:
        0 mmHg ... 300 mmHg
    meaning:
        0 mmHg ... 90 mmHg:
            meaning of value = "Low"
        91 mmHg ... 120 mmHg:
            meaning of value = "Normal"
    documentation:
        english: "The force of circulating blood."

<Status> is an enumeration:
    valid values:
        "Active"; "Inactive"; "Pending"
    reuse:
        reuse period of value is 1 day.

